The paper discusses the challenges of managing and analyzing private data in a secure data enclave, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of data science methods to analyze large amounts of data, which falls under the categories of databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper proposes a solution for enabling interactive analysis of sensitive data, which involves the use of Python language constructs and Jupyter notebooks, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE).
